It is a human that was transformed into a mollusc-like creature. Its shape and abilities were patterned after an object that was nearby during the transformation.

It is fed a nutrient broth suitable to humans. It hears and speaks either through the handset or through another normal phone that it is wired up to. The carapace is similar to an abalone shell and can be damaged. Its memory and knowledge has been tested the most, it has functioned for over 70 years. Even if it is voted into oblivion, it is slated to be a character in a Foundation Tale, and more details will surface eventually. If it survives the next few hours, I will update the entry with more information.







